metadata.name: Flight E721 #01
metadata.description:
Flight E721

Oh humans!
You are lost in your future
You are lost in your past
For present is just what you took as granted.

Time will fly-by and leaves nothing but regret
Oh humans!
You are lost in your future
You are lost in your past

Take that flight to chase what present has offered
Live today for everyday offers you rebirth
Live today while there is hope "

-sigmax











[ In life we hesitate in taking chances for what today has to offer considering that may be I will figure out tomorrow, But later ends in regret .
Present is beautiful & it defines you today, so work today to build for tomorrow; remember to live ]


Size : 3500x5000 pixels
Format : jpeg
